<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/mystic-bridge.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/mysticbridge.jpg" alt="Mystic Bridge / Ellen McIlwaine" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/mystic-bridge.php">Mystic Bridge<br />Ellen McIlwaine</a></h4><p>とにかく熱く歌い上げるスタイルに心をうたれてしまいます。アコースティックな楽器が中心で演奏されたライブ感溢れる1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000K2RD08?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000K2RD08" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Mystic Bridge-Ellen McIlwaine']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmystic-bridge%252Fid252810537%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Mystic Bridge-Ellen McIlwaine']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/knuckle-down.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/knuckledown.jpg" alt="Knuckle Down / Ani DiFranco" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/knuckle-down.php">Knuckle Down<br />Ani DiFranco</a></h4><p>女性らしい繊細な歌を聴かせてくれる「Ani DiFranco」の作品です。アコースティックなパンクとも言える熱のこもった演奏は何度も聴きたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0006SSQGG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0006SSQGG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Knuckle Down-Ani DiFranco']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fknuckle-down%252Fid41454096%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Knuckle Down-Ani DiFranco']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/nebular-for-thirteen.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nebularfor.jpg" alt="Nebular For Thirteen / Ngatari" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/nebular-for-thirteen.php">Nebular For Thirteen<br />Ngatari</a></h4><p>ジャズの影響が感じられる音楽です。ピアノの繊細な音を優しく包み込むような歌声が聴いているうちに悩みを吹き飛ばせてくれます。Massive Atacckのカヴァーなどもあり。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002ZW47GO?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002ZW47GO" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Nebular For Thirteen-Ngatari']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnebular-for-thirteen%252Fid353450609%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Nebular For Thirteen-Ngatari']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/labyrinth.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/labi.jpg" alt="Labyrinth / Takashi Wada" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/labyrinth.php">Labyrinth<br />Takashi Wada</a></h4><p>女性ヴォーカル作品ではないのですが、繊細な音と優しい音色は聴いているものの心を癒してくれます。疲れたときに聴きたい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002C006TG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002C006TG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Labyrinth-Takashi Wada']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Flabyrinth%252Fid324650484%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Labyrinth-Takashi Wada']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/hard-bossa.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/hardbossa.jpg" alt="Hard Bossa / Joyce" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/hard-bossa.php">Hard Bossa<br />Joyce</a></h4><p>勢いのある演奏と力がみなぎる歌に心を奪われてしまいます。ボサノヴァ持つパワーを感じることができる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00002MT6X?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00002MT6X" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Hard Bossa-Joyce']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fhard-bossa%252Fid32305505%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Hard Bossa-Joyce']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/ladies-of-the-canyon.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/ladiesofthe.jpg" alt="Ladies of the Canyon / Joni Mitchell" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/ladies-of-the-canyon.php">Ladies of the Canyon<br />Joni Mitchell</a></h4><p>人の心に潜む様々な感情を歌っているかのような音楽です。素晴らしい歌を聴いているうちに悩みや辛いことがいつの間にか吹き飛んでしまうでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000002KOQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000002KOQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Ladies of the Canyon-Joni Mitchell']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fladies-of-the-canyon%252Fid217611592%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Ladies of the Canyon-Joni Mitchell']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/souvenir.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/souvenil.jpg" alt="Souvenir / DOUBLE FAMOUS" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/souvenir.php">Souvenir<br />DOUBLE FAMOUS</a></h4><p>畠山美由紀の歌がフィーチャーされている作品。素晴らしい演奏と生演奏の素晴らしさを感じさせる名作です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005R13L?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005R13L" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Souvenir-DOUBLE FAMOUS']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fsouvenir%252Fid252318990%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Souvenir-DOUBLE FAMOUS']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/optimista.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/optimista.jpg" alt="Optimista / Michiru Monday" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/optimista.php">Optimista<br />Michiru Monday</a></h4><p>アコースティック＋エレクトリックと言った内容のヴォーカルアルバム。ラテンのご機嫌なサウンドを感じることができる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00001ZTIT?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00001ZTIT" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Optimista-Michiru Monday']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Foptimista%252Fid76115354%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Optimista-Michiru Monday']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/19.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/adele.jpg" alt="19 / ADELE" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/08/19.php">19<br />ADELE</a></h4><p>熟練されたヴォーカルスタイルが心地よい1枚。少ない楽器編成で堂々と歌い上げるスタイルにいつの間にか夢中になってしまうでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0018QOIXU?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0018QOIXU" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', '19-ADELE']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252F19-standard-edition%252Fid270409624%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', '19-ADELE']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

